	p These 2 templates moves the top edge of content area up to the very top of the page, allowing site header to overlay/overlap the content area. Templates work best with full-screen cover imagery.

	p The "light" and "dark" represent colors of text in overlaid header. Such overlaid header has no background.

	p Using these templates will remove page intro title section and there will be no <code>h1</code> heading tag added by the theme onto the page.

	p <em>These templates work with every public post type.</em>

